*1980年-[[阿兰·古斯|阿兰·古斯]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pbs.org/wnet/hawking/mysteries/html/guth_1.html |title=PBS Unsolved Mysteries |accessdate=2014-04-07 |archive-date=2014-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140813135016/http://www.pbs.org/wnet/hawking/mysteries/html/guth_1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/03/16/science/16cnd-cosmic.html?pagewanted=1&sq&st=cse%22alan%20guth%22&scp=3 |title=''New York Times'', March 16, 2006. "Scientists Get Glimpse of First Moments After Beginning of Time" |accessdate=2014-04-07 |archive-date=2013-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514085925/http://www.nytimes.com/2006/03/16/science/16cnd-cosmic.html?pagewanted=1&sq&st=cse%22alan%20guth%22&scp=3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>與斯塔罗宾斯基（Alexei Starobinsky）各自獨立提出[[宇宙暴漲|宇宙暴漲]]理論。
